summary: You know, if Detective Pikachu does launch a Pokémon Cinematic Universe and they end up doing an adaption of the Gen 1 games...
body: You know, if Detective Pikachu does launch a Pokémon Cinematic Universe and they end up doing an adaption of the Gen 1 games plot… I kind of want them to use Ash as the main character instead of Red, if only because Legendary would have literally no choice but to let Ash age and grow up if they kept him around for several live-action movies.

summary: when I first heard of detective Pikachu and that it was going to be live action/cgi pokemon I was so scared especially because...
body:
when I first heard of detective Pikachu and that it was going to be live action/cgi pokemon I was so scared

especially because of so many live action with cgi monsters/aliens/creatures based on something (books/shows etc) always have the bare minimum cgi characters.

but the detective Pikachu trailers have proven me wrong by showing so many pokemon in background shots and just, pokemon of all regions being in the movie (instead of maybe 10-20 pokemon all being from gen 1)

I am so excited for this movie
